---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Kenny Studio — 臺灣獨立 iOS App 工作室｜Mish、取貨吧、找廁所"
      description="Kenny Studio 是臺灣的一人 iOS 開發工作室，專注做好日常小工具：Mish（讀書筆記與閱讀紀錄）、取貨吧（包裹追蹤）、找廁所（全臺公廁地圖）。"
      current="home">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="google-site-verification" content="pKMjK0859MtcqL2gR8n0npRlkoIcC2j44IJpKHi6nPs" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://kenny324324.github.io/studioweb/" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Kenny Studio — 臺灣獨立 iOS App 工作室" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="專注做好日常小工具：Mish 讀書筆記、取貨吧包裹追蹤、找廁所公廁地圖。" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://kenny324324.github.io/studioweb/" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Kenny Studio" />
    <meta property="og:locale" content="zh_TW" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://kenny324324.github.io/studioweb/assets/MyLogo.png" />
    <script is:inline type="application/ld+json">
    {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Kenny Studio",
        "url": "https://kenny324324.github.io/studioweb/",
        "description": "臺灣獨立 iOS App 開發工作室，產品包括 Mish｜讀書筆記與閱讀紀錄、Pickup 取貨吧、FindToilets 找廁所。",
        "founder": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Kenny" },
        "email": "kenny4work324@gmail.com"
    }
    </script>
    <script is:inline async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9616816354780961" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero hero-brand">
    <div class="container-shell hero-grid">
      <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Kenny Studio · Taiwan Indie iOS Studio</p>
      <h1>把日常小事，做成好用的&nbsp;iOS&nbsp;App</h1>
      <p class="lede">Kenny Studio 是位於臺灣臺北的一人開發工作室。從閱讀紀錄、包裹追蹤到找公廁，每個 App 只專心解決一件具體的事：介面貼近 iOS 原生、尊重你的注意力，把小事做到順手。</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#apps">查看我們的 App</a>
        <a class="action-link" href="/studioweb/about/">了解 Kenny Studio</a>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true" data-motion="spatial">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/mish/sc1-320.avif" type="image/avif" />
          <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/mish/sc1-320.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img src="/studioweb/assets/mish/sc1-320.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="693" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/packagetracker/sc1-320.avif" type="image/avif" />
          <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/packagetracker/sc1-320.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img src="/studioweb/assets/packagetracker/sc1-320.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="693" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/findtoilet/sc1-320.avif?v=2" type="image/avif" />
          <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/findtoilet/sc1-320.webp?v=2" type="image/webp" />
          <img src="/studioweb/assets/findtoilet/sc1-320.jpg?v=2" alt="" width="320" height="693" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Apps -->
  <section class="section" id="apps">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">01 / Apps</p>
        <h2>三個 App，各自做好一件事</h2>
        <p>全部由 Kenny Studio 設計與開發（Apps by Kenny Studio），在 App Store 上架，繁體中文優先。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="product-grid">
        <article class="product-card">
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/mish/icon-160.avif?v=3" type="image/avif" />
            <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/mish/icon-160.webp?v=3" type="image/webp" />
            <img class="app-icon" src="/studioweb/assets/mish/icon-160.png?v=3" alt="" width="64" height="64" loading="lazy" />
          </picture>
          <h3>Mish</h3>
          <p class="product-claim">安靜地陪你讀完每一本書</p>
          <p class="product-desc">書櫃與書單管理、專注計時、讀書筆記與閱讀統計。不催你，也不評判你的進度。</p>
          <div class="product-links">
            <a class="action-link" href="/studioweb/mish/">認識 Mish</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="product-card">
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/packagetracker/icon-160.avif?v=3" type="image/avif" />
            <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/packagetracker/icon-160.webp?v=3" type="image/webp" />
            <img class="app-icon" src="/studioweb/assets/packagetracker/icon-160.png?v=3" alt="" width="64" height="64" loading="lazy" />
          </picture>
          <h3>取貨吧</h3>
          <p class="product-claim">所有包裹，一處掌握</p>
          <p class="product-desc">超商、宅配與國際快遞追蹤，AI 截圖辨識單號、到貨與取貨提醒、桌面小工具。</p>
          <div class="product-links">
            <a class="action-link" href="/studioweb/packagetracker/">認識取貨吧</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="product-card">
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/findtoilet/icon-160.avif?v=3" type="image/avif" />
            <source srcset="/studioweb/assets/findtoilet/icon-160.webp?v=3" type="image/webp" />
            <img class="app-icon" src="/studioweb/assets/findtoilet/icon-160.png?v=3" alt="" width="64" height="64" loading="lazy" />
          </picture>
          <h3>找廁所</h3>
          <p class="product-claim">快速找到附近適合的公共廁所</p>
          <p class="product-desc">全臺公廁地圖與清單，含評等、無障礙與親子設施資訊，支援中英日韓四種語言。</p>
          <div class="product-links">
            <a class="action-link" href="/studioweb/findtoilet/">認識找廁所</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 原則 -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">02 / Principles</p>
        <h2>工作室的三個原則</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-list">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <h3>解決具體的小事</h3>
          <p>不做「什麼都想做」的 App。每個產品都從一個真實、具體的日常麻煩開始，把那件事做到好用為止。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <h3>尊重注意力</h3>
          <p>不硬塞 onboarding、不濫發推播。打開 App 的第一秒，就能做你來做的那件事。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <h3>貼近原生的介面</h3>
          <p>以 SwiftUI 與原生框架開發，遵循 iOS 介面慣例。各產品的資料處理方式，如實寫在<a href="/studioweb/privacy/">各自的隱私政策</a>。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Guide -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">03 / Guide</p>
        <h2>精選文章</h2>
        <p>圍繞產品領域的實用攻略，以及一人工作室的開發札記。</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="post-list">
        <li>
          <a class="post-title" href="/studioweb/guide/taipei-station-toilet/">台北車站找廁所完整攻略：13 個最近最乾淨的選擇</a>
          <p class="post-excerpt">車站內、地下街、周邊百貨的 13 個公廁選項，標示位置、開放時間與無障礙狀況。</p>
          <p class="post-meta">公共廁所攻略 · 相關產品：<a href="/studioweb/findtoilet/">找廁所</a></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="post-title" href="/studioweb/guide/accessible-toilet/">全臺無障礙廁所使用指南：怎麼找、誰能用、常見誤解</a>
          <p class="post-excerpt">無障礙廁所的設計要求、法規標準與使用禮儀，寫給需要的人與想尊重設施的人。</p>
          <p class="post-meta">公共廁所攻略 · 相關產品：<a href="/studioweb/findtoilet/">找廁所</a></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="post-title" href="/studioweb/guide/solo-dev-first-year/">獨立 App 開發一年心得：從找廁所到取貨吧</a>
          <p class="post-excerpt">一人工作室做 iOS App 的第一年：產品怎麼選、時間怎麼分、收入從哪來。</p>
          <p class="post-meta">開發札記</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p><a class="action-link" href="/studioweb/guide/">瀏覽全部文章</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact / Trust -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">04 / Contact</p>
        <h2>聯絡與支援</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-list">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <h3>使用問題與回報</h3>
          <p>三個 App 的使用問題、錯誤回報與資料更正，都由 Kenny 本人回覆。<a href="/studioweb/contact/">前往支援頁</a>。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p><a href="mailto:kenny4work324@gmail.com">kenny4work324@gmail.com</a><br />一般事項 72 小時內回覆。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <h3>隱私政策</h3>
          <p>網站與各 App 的資料處理方式分別說明：<a href="/studioweb/privacy/">隱私政策總覽</a>。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
